#. module: yoga_pilates
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:yoga_pilates.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Customize the \"Contact Us\" form</strong>: Adjust on your Studio "
"Website, the form to handle specific requests such as corporate events or "
"wellbeing retreats."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Tilpas kontaktformularen</strong>: Tilpas formularen på dit studios "
"hjemmeside, så den kan håndtere specifikke forespørgsler, såsom "
"firmaarrangementer eller wellness-ophold."

#. module: yoga_pilates
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:yoga_pilates.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Define instructor expertise: </strong>In the <strong>Work "
"Information</strong> section of an employee, define employee's expertise by "
"using the <strong>Role</strong> field."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Angiv trænerens faglige kompetencer: </strong>Under <strong>"
"Arbejdsoplysninger</strong> for den pågældende medarbejder ved at udfylde "
"feltet <strong>Rolle</strong>."

#. module: yoga_pilates
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:yoga_pilates.welcome_article_body
msgid "<strong>Do you want to go further?</strong>"
msgstr "<strong>Vil du tage det et skridt videre?</strong>"

#. module: yoga_pilates
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:yoga_pilates.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Enable easy online bookings</strong>: Utilize <strong>eCommerce "
"features</strong> to set up online booking and secure payment options for "
"classes."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Gør det nemt at foretage online-reservationer</strong>: Brug <strong>"
